sequenceDiagram
    participant Monitor as 监控与控制面
    participant LB as 负载均衡
    participant AZA as AZ-A实例
    participant AZB as AZ-B实例
    participant AZC as AZ-C实例
    participant State as Redis/MQ/PG HA控制器

    Monitor->>Monitor: 检测AZ-A大面积失联
    LB->>AZA: 健康检查失败
    LB-->>AZA: 摘除流量
    LB->>AZB: 增加流量
    LB->>AZC: 增加流量

    State->>State: 选举Redis/MQ/PG替代节点
    State->>State: fencing旧主或旧Broker
    Monitor->>Monitor: 检查容量与复制状态

    alt 剩余容量充足且状态组件安全
        Monitor->>AZB: 保持NORMAL或SHED_LOAD
        Monitor->>AZC: 保持NORMAL或SHED_LOAD
    else 容量或同步副本不足
        Monitor->>AZB: SUBMIT_CLOSED
        Monitor->>AZC: SUBMIT_CLOSED
    end
